<div class="hboDetailRowNoBorder row">
</div>

<div class="hboDetailRow row">
    <div class="col-xs-12">
        <div class="headerStyle col-xs-12 col-sm-4">
            <strong>Example Questions Relating To Wills</strong>
        </div>
        <div class="fieldStyle col-xs-12 col-sm-8">
            <div class="topTFStyle col-xs-12">
                <ul>
                    <li>Have there been any significant changes that may mean the wills are not up to date?</li>
                    <li>Are the wills up to date?</li>
                    <li>Do they reflect your ongoing requirements?</li>
                    <li>Is your children's guardianship catered for in the will?</li>
                    <li>Do you own a foreign property? (A UK will may not be valid for a foreign realty)</li>
                    <li>Have your circumstances chaned since last updating your will?</li>
                    <li>Do you have a power of attorney in place? Is this a lasting or enduring arrangement?</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>


<div class="hboDetailRow row">
        <div class="col-xs-12">
